title: TuneIn Radio Pro - Live Radio V15.2.apk
description:
TuneIn Radio Pro - Live Radio v15.2

TuneIn is a new way to listen to the world through live local and global radio from wherever you are. Whether you want music, sports, news or current events, TuneIn offers over 50,000 stations and 1.2 million on-demand programs for you to choose from.

The TuneIn Radio Pro app for Android puts this entire experience in the palm of your hand with the added benefit of recording what youâ€™re listening to (requires memory card).

Important Update: This new version of TuneIn (15.2) includes Car Mode, which lets you listen to your favorite music, sports and news simply by speaking a command into your Android phone or tablet. This update also includes extra large buttons for easy viewing and control.

What's in this version : (Updated : March 31, 2016)
Bug fixes and improvements
Multi SKU Upsell
Fix for keyboard not showing in search
Exit the sign in/sign up screen after logging out
Restyled sign up flow
Fix for purchasing songs from your profile
